53
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:57,840
and specific areas of the brain

54
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:00,120
that are activated
during those meditations

55
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,910
change our way of being
in fundamental ways,

56
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:04,890
not just during the meditation practice,

57
