816
00:30:58,620 --> 00:30:59,670
while talking to somebody,

817
00:30:59,670 --> 00:31:00,930
in fact, you're not even listening

818
00:31:00,930 --> 00:31:02,280
to what they're saying at all.

819
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:04,470
Okay? So you have two
spotlights of perception.

820
00:31:04,470 --> 00:31:07,560
You can split them or merge them into one.

821
00:31:07,560 --> 00:31:09,510
And, this is very important,

822
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:13,050
those spotlights of perception
can intensify or dim,

823
00:31:13,050 --> 00:31:14,730
and there, I'm using analogy.

824
00:31:14,730 --> 00:31:17,700
What I mean by that is your
perception of what's happening

825
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:21,930
within those spotlights can
be very, very high acuity.

826
00:31:21,930 --> 00:31:25,110
That is, you can register
very fine changes in detail

827
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:28,410
like tingling on one side of
your big toe of your right foot

828
00:31:28,410 --> 00:31:29,460
versus the other,

829
00:31:29,460 --> 00:31:31,170
or it can be somewhat more diffuse.

830
00:31:31,170 --> 00:31:32,670
You're just thinking about your whole toe,

831
00:31:32,670 --> 00:31:34,500
which, in that case,
seems like a small area,

832
00:31:34,500 --> 00:31:38,820
but the point is that you can
consciously adjust the acuity,

833
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:41,820
that is, the fineness of your perception.

834
00:31:41,820 --> 00:31:43,620
All of this is under your power

835
00:31:43,620 --> 00:31:46,470
because of the incredible
ability of a brain structure

836
00:31:46,470 --> 00:31:48,990
whose name you now understand and know,

837
00:31:48,990 --> 00:31:51,870
which is the left dorsolateral
prefrontal cortex,

838
00:31:51,870 --> 00:31:53,460
although there are other
areas of your brain

839
00:31:53,460 --> 00:31:54,630
involved as well.

840
00:31:54,630 --> 00:31:58,170
Your ability to direct your
attention to specific things

841
00:31:58,170 --> 00:32:00,510
in your environment or within your body

842
00:32:00,510 --> 00:32:03,660
or to split those points
