1784
01:08:53,220 --> 01:08:56,310
Now, I'm a big fan of some
of the newer meditation apps

1785
01:08:56,310 --> 01:08:57,143
that are out there.

1786
01:08:57,143 --> 01:08:58,557
One in particular that I've been using

1787
01:08:58,557 --> 01:09:00,210
