1799
01:09:27,060 --> 01:09:28,140
I think it's terrific,

1800
01:09:28,140 --> 01:09:29,970
and I think one of the
reasons it's terrific

1801
01:09:29,970 --> 01:09:32,189
is that Sam includes short descriptions

1802
01:09:32,189 --> 01:09:33,776
of what meditation is doing

1803
01:09:33,777 --> 01:09:36,600
and what a specific
