1804
01:09:36,600 --> 01:09:38,729
just prior to doing that meditation.

1805
01:09:38,729 --> 01:09:40,409
So those meditations can be quite brief.

1806
01:09:40,410 --> 01:09:42,300
Some of them are a minute
long, two minutes long,

1807
01:09:42,300 --> 01:09:45,149
some are longer or even
quite a bit longer.

1808
01:09:45,149 --> 01:09:48,119
That app, I think, includes
a variety of meditations

1809
01:09:48,120 --> 01:09:52,050
that really encompasses the
huge range of possibilities

1810
01:09:52,050 --> 01:09:53,700
that are possible with meditation,

1811
01:09:53,700 --> 01:09:57,240
and that, at least by my
experience of the Waking Up app,

1812
01:09:57,240 --> 01:10:00,840
has led to my most consistent
meditation practice.

1813
